
After installing Lampp/Xampp in linux go to htdoc folder

1. mkdir ruhi
2. cd ruhi
3. git clone git://github.com/zendframework/ZendSkeletonApplication.git
4. mv ZendSkeletonApplication/* .
5. rm -fr ZendSkeletonApplication/
6. curl -s https://getcomposer.org/installer | php --
7. composer require zendframework/zendframework

Incase if you see composer not part of command or somrtimes it will prompt you for installing/downloading composer
Go ahead and say Y to download/install OR mannually install composer inside folder ruhi
